        "timestamp": "2018-10-09 00:29:30.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4: Code-Review-2\n\nWhere is this being run right now? Will it be run in CSIT?\n\nThese seem like integration tests to me rather than unit tests. Please rename appropriately.\n\nPlease generate the ipass, sopin and upin gpg files instead of checking them into the repo. If you really them in the repo. Use the text format or base64 encoding and then convert to gpg during runtime. We cannot check-in binary files into the repo.",
        "patchset_number": 4
      },
